  "title": "⚡GET PAID TO CONNECT",
  "description": "<p><em>Events & Sales Ambassador | Training & Mentorship Provided</em></p><p>Step into a high-energy <strong>Events & Sales</strong> role where your people skills turn into real income. No experience needed — you’ll receive <strong>daily 1-on-1 training and mentorship</strong> while gaining hands-on experience representing established brands.</p><p>⸻</p><p>💼<strong> What You’ll Do</strong></p><p>• Engage customers through brand activations, events & roadshows</p><p>• Represent clients at expos, promotions & campaigns</p><p>• Build strong communication & presentation skills</p><p>• Work closely with a supportive, high-energy team</p><p>⸻</p><p>👀<strong> Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>• Positive attitude, disciplined & eager to learn</p><p>• Good interpersonal & communication skills</p><p>• Fresh grads, ORD personnel & career switchers welcome</p><p>• Retail / events / F&B / promoter experience is a plus</p><p>⸻</p><p>🚀<strong> Why Join Us</strong></p><p>• Uncapped earnings (avg <strong>$30K–$50K/year</strong>)</p><p>• No experience required — full training provided</p><p>• Daily 1-on-1 coaching & mentorship</p><p>• Fast-track career progression (Management Trainee path)</p><p>• Fun, supportive team culture</p><p>⸻</p><p>✨ No desk-bound work. No getting overlooked.</p><p>Just real growth, recognition, and opportunities to level up.</p><p>📩 <strong>Interested?</strong></p><p>Send us your CV (photo optional).</p>",
